{"tid":2188537,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"洗米華講緊賭場實名制 根本係nothing new","createTime":"2020-09-04T09:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:49:38.000Z","uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ddc6682041105347197fb6343ceb77ae545f96","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"首先佢講嘅係marker實名制<br />\n本身你去賭場借錢都已經係實名制<br />\n會紀錄你身分證或護照<br />\n好多富豪係用自己下屬ID去做<br />\n所以所謂marker實名制根本多餘<br />\n<br />\n存響太陽城嘅deposit <br />\n亦都係一定要賭一兩轉先至拎得出<br />\n否則唔會俾你提款證明 轉唔到入銀行<br />\n存款取款亦都係實名制<br />\n<br />\n真心講實名制就學英國或坡狗<br />\n係入場實名制<br />\n喺門口已經影相 check Passport<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再wewewawa<br />\n你覺得真係咁大影響其他賭場唔開聲<br />\n咪咁幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b5502ba9a6a0477a1b1435bd376b3ed0c73b3a","tid":2188537,"uid":77717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YOnoPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YOnoPa.png&h=9e4f0f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知邊個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1f336d12e38a55f0e7ccc82a12e6b0db3837de","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b5502ba9a6a0477a1b1435bd376b3ed0c73b3a","tid":2188537,"uid":77717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YOnoPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YOnoPa.png&h=9e4f0f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知邊個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"真係賭場底層或細客<br />\n先會拎得出一封notice去評論<br />\n賭場用跟班做CDD出marker不嬲都係<br />\nCDD份盡職調查只要係pass/fail<br />\n俾幾多marker係賭場管理層去訂<br />\n<br />\n所以封信根本冇講過任何野<br />\n只係講客人一定要過CDD"},{"pid":"c8cb9c4b6af8d719223febfc8e9b0822a51a0979","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"同你地講解下實名制有唔同層次<br />\n<br />\n洗米華講緊係marker貸款實名制<br />\n另外有一種係新加坡/英國vip入場已經要實名登記<br />\n<br />\n道理上入得貴賓廳嘅<br />\n都應該通過CDD客戶盡職調查<br />\n但係通過CDD並唔會話你知可以借幾多錢<br />\n所以到底借幾多錢比個客係賭場管理層決定<br />\n同前述實名制冇關係<br />\n好多係用二打六去過CDD但會貸幾千萬或過億<br />\n<br />\n所以洗米華講緊嘅貸款實名制<br />\n本身已經行緊 真係nothing new <br />\n<br />\n有興趣想知先再同大家講多啲"},{"pid":"15b858a5245458a8352f375fccc6f3ca201ef077","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"其實仲有諗吓其他賭場一句都冇講過<br />\n就知係nothing new<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好因為唔熟賭場而以為係新改革<br />\n澳門係奶共天堂"},{"pid":"0daeaae4647c9cc5312d37600fd96c035dace867","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"有啲人話做唔到大數<br />\n其實都係唔熟做法<br />\n<br />\n如果一個貪官想借5千萬去賭<br />\n賭場會將自己已經洗乾淨嘅10個𡃁<br />\n每人登記5百萬去湊夠5千萬<br />\n<br />\n有人話唔用本人冇法律效用<br />\n本身支那禁賭 <br />\n所以所有賭場貸款都係冇得嚮支那法庭追究<br />\n實際賭場會用個人對個人貸款比支那人<br />\n所以上述例子中係有10份個人貸款合同"},{"pid":"0cbc474c38810c5c3adf03c729fa2f8ae806c1db","tid":2188537,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"你咩都後門，圖又冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入過廳賭未啊"},{"pid":"fbf888e417fcf1a1ba8b71101550ab7a1b1cd77f","tid":2188537,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbc474c38810c5c3adf03c729fa2f8ae806c1db","tid":2188537,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"你咩都後門，圖又冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"